Package de.esoco.ewt.layout

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LayoutFactory
    A factory interface that creates container layouts.
    LayoutMapper
    An interface for the mapping of EWT layouts to other layout instances after their creation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContentLayout
    A layout class for typical content area in application.
    DefaultLayoutFactory
    The default layout factory implementation for GEWT.
    DockLayout
    A dock layout that allows to add components on the four sides or in the center.
    EdgeLayout
    A generic layout implementation similar to the AWT BorderLayout but with the additional possibility to add components to the edges.
    FillLayout
    A layout implementation similar to the SWT FillLayout.
    FlexLayout
    A CSS flex layout implementation.
    FlowLayout
    A flow layout implementation.
    FluentCssLayout<L extends FluentCssLayout<L>>
    A base class for CSS-based layouts that implement a fluent interface for the layout configuration.
    FormLayout
    A layout that arranges components in an input form.
    GenericLayout
    Base class for all EWT layouts.
    GridLayout
    A CSS grid layout implementation.
    GroupLayout
    A layout that groups components with an optional title/caption.
    LayoutMapper.IdentityLayoutMapper
    A default layout mapper implementation that always returns the original layout.
    ListLayout
    A list layout implementation.
    MenuLayout
    A panel layout that contains a menu or navigation structure.
    TableGridLayout
    A table-based grid layout.
    TwoLayerLayout
    A base class for layouts that contain two layers of GWT panels.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FlexLayout.ItemAlignment
    Enumeration of the flex layout item alignments.
    FlexLayout.Wrapping
    Enumeration of the flex layout wrapping modes.
